OL,3,CAirbus workers to stage strikes amid
OL,4,Cpay dispute
OL,6,FWorkers at aircraft manufacturer
OL,7,FAirbus are to stage a series of
OL,8,Fstrikes in a dispute over pay.
OL,10,FUnite said around 3,000 of its members
OL,11,Fwill walk out for 10 days in September
OL,12,Fafter they voted overwhelmingly in
OL,13,Ffavour of industrial action.
OL,15,FThe Unite members are based in
OL,16,FBroughton, north Wales, and Filton,
OL,17,Fnear Bristol.
