OL,3,CAirbus workers to stage strikes amid
OL,4,Cpay dispute
OL,6,FUnite general secretary Sharon Graham
OL,7,Fsaid: "Airbus is generating billions
OL,8,Fin profit; workers deserve a fair
OL,9,Fdeal. Our members are simply seeking
OL,10,Ffairness not favours.
OL,12,F"Airbus workers have the total support
OL,13,Fof their union in this dispute."
OL,15,FUnite warned the strikes will hit
OL,16,Fproduction of wings for Airbus's
OL,17,Fcommercial and military aircraft
OL,18,Fprogrammes.
