OL,3,CAirbus workers to stage strikes amid
OL,4,Cpay dispute
OL,6,FSue Partridge, Airbus UK country
OL,7,Fmanager commercial aircraft, said: "We
OL,8,Fhave made a competitive and fair pay
OL,9,Foffer in 2025 that builds on the
OL,10,Fstrong foundations of pay increases
OL,11,Ftotalling over 20% in the last three
OL,12,Fyears and a #2,644 bonus payment made
OL,13,Fin April this year.
OL,15,F"Our priority remains to find a
OL,16,Fresolution together with the trade
OL,17,Funion that ensures the long-term
OL,18,Fcompetitiveness and success of Airbus
OL,19,Fin the UK."
